In 2013, Fritz released Dad Country, his third album overall and his first under the name "Jonny Fritz", on ATO Records.
It was followed by the release of the album's single "Goodbye Summer", for which a music video was also made.
Fritz released his fourth studio album, Sweet Creep, October 14, 2016.
Rolling Stone named the album #14 in their 40 best country records of 2016.
Fritz performed at SXSW in 2012 and 2014.
